This is Data::ConveyorBelt.

INSTALLATION

Data::ConveyorBelt installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell
is set up, you should just be able to do

    % perl -MCPAN -e 'install Data::ConveyorBelt'

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

Data::ConveyorBelt documentation is available in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc Data::ConveyorBelt

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

